      "inputs": ["bundle", "context"],
      "outputs": ["prompt", "images"],
      "config": {
        "prompt": {
          "template": "Translate PRODUCT PARAMETERS from English to Polish.\nProduct name: \"{{title}}\"\nParameters JSON: {{parameters}}\n\nRules:\n1. Return ONLY valid JSON.\n2. Output schema: {\"parameters\":[{\"parameterId\":\"<existing id>\",\"value\":\"<translated value>\"}]}.\n3. Keep each parameterId exactly as provided.\n4. Translate only user-facing values to Polish.\n5. Keep model numbers, brand names, SKUs, and units unchanged when they should stay literal.\n6. Preserve pipe delimiters for multi-value text, for example \"Red|Blue\" to \"Czerwony|Niebieski\".\n7. Return one row for each input row that has both parameterId and a non-empty value.\n8. No markdown, no code fences, no explanations."
        }
      }
    },
